<p>The Planter is part of the supply production of your colony. The Planter will plant and harvest sugar cane, bamboo, or cactus.</p>

<p>The Planter can also craft paper, books, sugar, and anything made with bamboo. The Planter will only make these items when they have been taught the recipes, receive a request for an item, and have the needed materials.</p>

<p><strong>Note:</strong> The Planter can only learn a set number of recipes based on their hut level. So:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Hut Level</th>
      <th>Recipes</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
